<!doctype html><html lang="pt-BR"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>Configuração inicial REIVILO</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/admin.css"></head><body class="login-page"><section class="login-card" style="width:min(760px,100%)"><h1>Configuração inicial</h1><p>Crie o acesso do painel e defina os dados básicos da mentoria. Tudo ficará salvo no PostgreSQL.</p><% if(error){ %><div class="alert"><%= error %></div><% } %><form method="post" class="stacked"><label>Usuário<input name="username" value="admin" required></label><label>Senha<input type="password" name="password" minlength="8" required></label><label>Confirmar senha<input type="password" name="confirm_password" minlength="8" required></label><label>Nome do produto<input name="product_name" value="Mentoria REIVILO" required></label><label>Valor da mentoria<input name="price_brl" value="997,00" required></label><label>Site<input name="site_url" value="https://www.reivilo.com.br"></label><label>ID do grupo do WhatsApp<input name="group_jid" placeholder="120363...@g.us"></label><label>Link de convite do grupo<input name="group_invite_link" placeholder="https://chat.whatsapp.com/..."></label><button class="primary" type="submit">Salvar e entrar</button></form></section></body></html>
